OL,3,CCelebrating Scotland's national poet
OL,4,CRobert Burns
OL,6,FDuring his 37 years he created some of
OL,7,Fthe world's most enduring works of
OL,8,Fpoetry and song.
OL,10,FWe have many great writers in the
OL,11,Fsouth of Scotland but Robert Burns was
OL,12,Finternationally recognised.
OL,14,FEllisland Farm was Robert Burns' first
OL,15,FDumfriesshire home. It was a place
OL,16,Fwhere he would pen some of his most
OL,17,Ffamous work.
