OL,6,FSince 2020 the farm has been under the
OL,7,Fcustodianship of a trust, dedicated to
OL,8,Fpreserving the site and preserving the
OL,9,Funique story of the bard.
OL,11,FJoan McCalpine, The Robert Burns
OL,12,FEllisland Trust said: "Robert Burns
OL,13,Fcame to Ellisland actually from
OL,14,FEdinburgh. His first book of poetry
OL,15,Fwas published and he was a bit of a
OL,16,Frock star really.
OL,18,F"He could have stayed in Edinburgh but
OL,19,Fhe wanted to get back to his roots. He
OL,20,Fwas offered the opportunity of
OL,21,Fbuilding a new farm as a tenant farmer.
