OL,3,CCelebrating Scotland's national poet
OL,4,CRobert Burns
OL,6,F"He chose Ellisland because it was the
OL,7,Fmost beautiful outlook and the most
OL,8,Finspiring outlook. That is why it is
OL,9,Fknown as the poet's choice.
OL,11,F"The land here was very challenging
OL,12,Fand it was very dry. He wanted
OL,13,Fsecurity for his family, a pension for
OL,14,Fhis family.
OL,16,F"Jean Armour was his wife and his life
OL,17,Fpartner and was incredibly loyal to
OL,18,Fhim. Most people know he had a
OL,19,Fcomplicated love life. She had a
OL,20,Fbeautiful voice and knew many songs
OL,21,Fand stories.
