OL,3,CCelebrating Scotland's national poet
OL,4,CRobert Burns
OL,6,F"The thing about Burns particularly
OL,7,Fwhen he moved to Ellisland he wasn't
OL,8,Fjust writing his own material he was
OL,9,Fcollecting the songs and stories of
OL,10,FScotland that he felt were endangered.
OL,11,FJean was one of the those people who
OL,12,Freally had the knowledge of the
OL,13,Fculture in her head and he really
OL,14,Fvalued that."
